WEBVTT


00:01:22.319 --> 00:01:23.400
Don't mess around.

00:01:28.760 --> 00:01:30.120
First come, first served.

00:01:30.239 --> 00:01:31.439
Brother Chengwen is mine.

00:01:32.159 --> 00:01:33.560
Saying he's yours doesn't make it true.

00:01:38.519 --> 00:01:39.200
Come on.

00:01:39.400 --> 00:01:40.239
What are you doing?

00:01:40.400 --> 00:01:41.959
What's the point of arguing over this?

00:01:42.040 --> 00:01:42.959
In the end,

00:01:42.959 --> 00:01:44.359
doesn't it depend on who he chooses?

00:01:46.560 --> 00:01:47.359
Alright.

00:01:47.439 --> 00:01:48.359
Stop arguing.

00:01:49.239 --> 00:01:50.519
Xuejiao was just talking to me

00:01:50.519 --> 00:01:51.519
about the South City project.

00:01:51.519 --> 00:01:52.719
I believe you two

00:01:52.719 --> 00:01:53.760
are here for the same reason, right?

00:01:53.959 --> 00:01:54.760
Brother Chengwen,

00:01:54.920 --> 00:01:56.640
I trust you one hundred percent.

00:01:56.640 --> 00:01:57.640
But

00:01:57.640 --> 00:01:58.840
Grandpa wants to know your real plan.

00:01:58.840 --> 00:01:59.760
My dad

00:01:59.760 --> 00:02:00.760
feels the same way.

00:02:00.760 --> 00:02:02.200
What real plan?

00:02:02.319 --> 00:02:04.000
I just want to squander that 50 billion.

00:02:04.319 --> 00:02:05.799
Why are you all making such a fuss?

00:02:05.799 --> 00:02:07.000
This is a money-losing project.

00:02:07.000 --> 00:02:07.920
Don't you get it?

00:02:09.240 --> 00:02:09.840
Forget it.

00:02:09.840 --> 00:02:11.520
I won't let you lose money.

00:02:15.719 --> 00:02:16.039
Hello?

00:02:16.039 --> 00:02:16.759
Shihan,

00:02:16.759 --> 00:02:17.520
immediately

00:02:17.520 --> 00:02:19.800
draft three South City project guarantee contracts and bring them here.

00:02:20.400 --> 00:02:21.199
Yes.

00:02:21.560 --> 00:02:22.360
Three copies.

00:02:31.919 --> 00:02:33.159
I've signed the guarantee contracts.

00:02:33.520 --> 00:02:34.479
Take them home

00:02:34.479 --> 00:02:35.240
and report back.

00:02:38.360 --> 00:02:39.159
You can go now.

00:02:43.800 --> 00:02:44.560
Young Master,

00:02:44.560 --> 00:02:46.319
that little security guard named Gu is here again.

00:02:48.360 --> 00:02:49.159
Hurry!

00:02:49.159 --> 00:02:50.319
Go hide in the room!

00:02:50.400 --> 00:02:50.960
Don't make a sound.

00:02:50.960 --> 00:02:51.560
Absolutely do not make a sound.

00:02:51.560 --> 00:02:51.840
Zhao Gang,

00:02:51.840 --> 00:02:52.560
take them inside.

00:02:52.560 --> 00:02:52.919
Go!

00:02:52.919 --> 00:02:53.439
Hurry inside!

00:02:53.439 --> 00:02:53.719
Come on.

00:02:53.719 --> 00:02:54.520
You go in too.

00:02:54.759 --> 00:02:55.560
This way.

00:03:13.719 --> 00:03:14.719
Brother Zhan Tian,

00:03:14.719 --> 00:03:16.319
you really are a rare genius.

00:03:17.000 --> 00:03:18.319
Your injuries healed so quickly.

00:03:19.319 --> 00:03:20.960
Seeing as we are of the same kind,

00:03:21.919 --> 00:03:23.159
let's have a couple of drinks together.

00:03:26.439 --> 00:03:27.240
Same kind?

00:03:27.800 --> 00:03:29.439
I'm just a nobody.

00:03:30.039 --> 00:03:31.759
How could I be worthy of being

00:03:31.759 --> 00:03:32.800
the same kind as Brother Zhan Tian?

00:03:35.560 --> 00:03:36.360
Alright.

00:03:37.039 --> 00:03:38.840
Kill me or torture me, do as you please.

00:03:39.360 --> 00:03:40.319
I only ask

00:03:40.319 --> 00:03:41.919
that Brother Zhan Tian makes it quick.

00:03:42.400 --> 00:03:43.919
Killing you

00:03:44.439 --> 00:03:45.360
would be a piece of cake.

00:03:45.759 --> 00:03:47.199
But I've always been curious.

00:03:47.599 --> 00:03:49.400
Why do you always go against me?

00:03:50.120 --> 00:03:50.759
If I

00:03:50.759 --> 00:03:51.919
were to tell you

00:03:51.960 --> 00:03:53.759
that I never wanted to go against you,

00:03:53.759 --> 00:03:54.560
would you believe me?

00:03:56.360 --> 00:03:58.039
It's those four female leads.

00:03:59.719 --> 00:04:00.759
Namely,

00:04:00.759 --> 00:04:01.439
Leng Qingqiu,

00:04:02.120 --> 00:04:05.360
along with Xu Xuejiao, Jiang Shihan, and Chen Mengyun.

00:04:06.159 --> 00:04:07.960
They're the ones who lost their minds.

00:04:08.360 --> 00:04:09.400
I don't know what's going on,

00:04:09.560 --> 00:04:10.759
but they just keep pestering me.

00:04:12.039 --> 00:04:13.960
So you didn't go against me?

00:04:14.240 --> 00:04:15.439
Me, go against you?

00:04:15.599 --> 00:04:17.439
Then I'd really be out of my mind, okay?

00:04:17.639 --> 00:04:19.199
Brother Zhan Tian, you're so powerful!

00:04:19.759 --> 00:04:21.120
You're the God of War of the Border,

00:04:21.439 --> 00:04:22.439
the Chosen One.

00:04:22.920 --> 00:04:24.199
Anyone who goes against you

00:04:24.199 --> 00:04:26.040
ends up dying a miserable death.

00:04:26.360 --> 00:04:27.519
In all sorts of bizarre ways.

00:04:27.560 --> 00:04:28.360
Lu Chengwen,

00:04:28.519 --> 00:04:29.120
I actually thought

00:04:29.120 --> 00:04:30.759
you were a worthy opponent,

00:04:31.040 --> 00:04:31.639
or even

00:04:31.639 --> 00:04:33.519
an excellent partner.

00:04:35.120 --> 00:04:36.120
I didn't expect

00:04:37.800 --> 00:04:38.720
you to be such a

00:04:38.720 --> 00:04:40.319
useless piece of trash.

00:04:41.920 --> 00:04:43.240
Ah, yes, yes, yes.

00:04:43.399 --> 00:04:44.519
I am trash.

00:04:44.600 --> 00:04:45.399
Enough.

00:04:45.560 --> 00:04:46.959
Just hurry up and kill me.

00:04:47.240 --> 00:04:49.319
I really can't go on with this plot anymore.

00:04:49.360 --> 00:04:50.240
I'm tired.

00:04:57.920 --> 00:04:58.240
Chengwen!

00:05:00.160 --> 00:05:01.000
Brother Zhao,

00:05:01.040 --> 00:05:02.560
just let us out!

00:05:02.560 --> 00:05:03.319
Get out of the way!

00:05:03.319 --> 00:05:04.600
We need to go save Brother Chengwen!

00:05:05.240 --> 00:05:06.040
Zhao Gang,

00:05:06.040 --> 00:05:07.800
as Brother Chengwen's personal bodyguard,

00:05:07.920 --> 00:05:09.040
is it competent of you to do this?

00:05:09.120 --> 00:05:09.920
No.

00:05:10.040 --> 00:05:11.560
The young master said to keep you here,

00:05:11.920 --> 00:05:13.000
he must have his reasons.

00:05:21.720 --> 00:05:23.319
Who said I was going to kill you?

00:05:24.759 --> 00:05:25.800
You're not going to kill me?

00:05:25.920 --> 00:05:27.360
If you're determined to die,

00:05:28.439 --> 00:05:30.000
I can grant your wish.

00:05:31.560 --> 00:05:32.360
Don't.

00:05:32.920 --> 00:05:34.160
Who doesn't want to live?

00:05:34.360 --> 00:05:36.120
You should've said earlier you wouldn't kill me.

00:05:36.240 --> 00:05:37.720
Thank you for sparing my life, Brother Zhan Tian.

00:05:37.959 --> 00:05:38.800
If you don't kill me,

00:05:38.800 --> 00:05:40.040
I'll do whatever you ask.

00:05:40.120 --> 00:05:40.959
Really.

00:05:42.639 --> 00:05:43.439
Good.

00:05:44.199 --> 00:05:45.000
First,

00:05:46.319 --> 00:05:47.920
give me back that five billion.

00:05:48.000 --> 00:05:48.600
Okay.

00:05:48.600 --> 00:05:49.399
No problem.

00:05:49.560 --> 00:05:50.519
I'll return it to you right away.

00:05:50.920 --> 00:05:51.720
But,

00:05:52.040 --> 00:05:53.240
you have to tell Leng Tianhao

00:05:53.240 --> 00:05:54.360
not to remove

00:05:54.360 --> 00:05:55.079
Leng Qingqiu

00:05:55.079 --> 00:05:56.000
from her CEO position.

00:05:56.199 --> 00:05:57.000
Second,

00:05:57.000 --> 00:05:58.519
I want you to take the lead in breaking the contract

00:05:58.759 --> 00:06:00.560
and withdraw funds from the South City project.

00:06:00.839 --> 00:06:02.199
Let this project fail.

00:06:03.759 --> 00:06:04.560
Why?

00:06:04.720 --> 00:06:05.519
Why?

00:06:05.959 --> 00:06:07.639
Because I want to unify Haicheng.

00:06:07.800 --> 00:06:09.199
So the Lu family cannot fall.

00:06:09.759 --> 00:06:11.519
And the four major families definitely cannot fall.

00:06:12.000 --> 00:06:14.519
What I want is a complete,

00:06:14.600 --> 00:06:15.800
or even stronger,

00:06:15.839 --> 00:06:17.560
more financially robust Haicheng.

00:06:17.959 --> 00:06:19.120
Not a piece of trash.

00:06:22.639 --> 00:06:23.959
I can agree to anything else,

00:06:24.000 --> 00:06:25.240
but withdrawing from the South City project

00:06:25.240 --> 00:06:26.160
is absolutely out of the question.

00:06:26.199 --> 00:06:27.399
Do you know

00:06:27.399 --> 00:06:29.720
that those civilians had their houses demolished

00:06:29.800 --> 00:06:31.360
and haven't received any compensation?

00:06:31.439 --> 00:06:32.040
Yes,

00:06:32.040 --> 00:06:32.959
there is temporary housing.

00:06:32.959 --> 00:06:33.680
But right now,

00:06:33.680 --> 00:06:34.800
the project has been halted.

00:06:34.920 --> 00:06:36.160
They have nowhere to live

00:06:36.160 --> 00:06:38.079
and can only stay in those temporary houses.

00:06:38.240 --> 00:06:38.879
Do you know

00:06:38.879 --> 00:06:40.680
how awful the conditions are in those temporary houses?

00:06:40.959 --> 00:06:42.959
They're worse than the worst urban villages.

00:06:42.959 --> 00:06:44.160
Even dirtier and messier.

00:06:44.439 --> 00:06:45.759
Do you know about these things,

00:06:45.759 --> 00:06:47.319
how many families have been torn apart,

00:06:47.319 --> 00:06:48.360
and left homeless?

00:06:49.040 --> 00:06:49.800
Brother Zhan Tian,

00:06:49.800 --> 00:06:51.399
you're the righteous male lead.

00:06:51.519 --> 00:06:52.480
You definitely wouldn't

00:06:52.480 --> 00:06:53.399
just watch this happen

00:06:53.399 --> 00:06:54.720
and do nothing, right?

00:06:57.319 --> 00:06:58.120
No.

00:06:59.000 --> 00:07:00.120
Do you

00:07:00.120 --> 00:07:01.360
have some misunderstanding about me?

00:07:01.959 --> 00:07:03.720
In my eyes,

00:07:03.720 --> 00:07:05.360
they are nothing but ants.

00:07:05.839 --> 00:07:07.399
Whether they suffer injustice

00:07:07.600 --> 00:07:08.560
in life,

00:07:08.560 --> 00:07:09.839
or whether they can survive,

00:07:10.240 --> 00:07:11.399
what does it have to do with me?

00:07:12.160 --> 00:07:12.959
No,

00:07:14.040 --> 00:07:15.720
how could you be this kind of person?

00:07:15.720 --> 00:07:16.519
Cut the crap.

00:07:18.160 --> 00:07:19.600
I'll ask you one more time.

00:07:20.000 --> 00:07:22.399
Are you withdrawing from the South City project?

00:07:23.360 --> 00:07:24.439
Withdraw,

00:07:24.439 --> 00:07:25.560
or not?

00:07:30.399 --> 00:07:31.759
Then let me tell you,

00:07:31.800 --> 00:07:33.000
what if I don't withdraw?

00:07:33.160 --> 00:07:34.800
Then think about your family.

00:07:36.120 --> 00:07:37.120
Your parents,

00:07:37.519 --> 00:07:38.920
and your friends.

00:07:39.519 --> 00:07:41.360
I just need to crook my finger,

00:07:41.759 --> 00:07:43.959
and they will disappear from this world.

00:07:44.199 --> 00:07:45.759
Just a crook of my finger.

00:07:46.199 --> 00:07:47.439
Do you understand?

00:07:53.519 --> 00:07:54.959
You're a smart man.

00:07:55.240 --> 00:07:56.399
You should know

00:07:57.040 --> 00:07:58.360
that whatever I want to do,

00:07:58.360 --> 00:08:00.120
no one can stop me.

00:08:00.839 --> 00:08:02.199
The plan to integrate Haicheng,

00:08:02.959 --> 00:08:04.160
you've had it figured out from the start.

00:08:04.160 --> 00:08:04.600
Is that so?

00:08:04.600 --> 00:08:06.240
I'll start by devouring the Leng family,

00:08:07.439 --> 00:08:08.600
then the Xu family,

00:08:08.959 --> 00:08:09.959
and the Chen family.

00:08:11.160 --> 00:08:11.959
Finally,

00:08:12.839 --> 00:08:14.920
they will all become my subordinates.

00:08:15.439 --> 00:08:16.759
Leng Qingqiu

00:08:16.759 --> 00:08:18.360
will become my servant.

00:08:19.639 --> 00:08:20.959
And Xu Xuejiao,

00:08:21.439 --> 00:08:22.399
Chen Mengyun,

00:08:23.600 --> 00:08:25.120
as well as

00:08:25.120 --> 00:08:26.920
that Jiang Shihan by your side.

00:08:30.560 --> 00:08:31.759
What about the Lu family?

00:08:32.000 --> 00:08:34.039
After I take over the Dasheng Group,

00:08:34.399 --> 00:08:36.720
I will make you and your family

00:08:36.720 --> 00:08:38.960
bear a massive debt you can never repay.

00:08:39.360 --> 00:08:40.720
When that time comes,

00:08:40.720 --> 00:08:42.519
if you are begging on the streets,

00:08:42.759 --> 00:08:43.759
maybe

00:08:43.759 --> 00:08:45.360
I'll give you some spare change.

00:08:45.639 --> 00:08:46.440
Of course,

00:08:48.120 --> 00:08:50.399
if you're willing to be my dog,

00:08:50.919 --> 00:08:54.039
I'll still leave some scraps for you.

00:08:58.919 --> 00:09:00.120
Provoking you like this,

00:09:00.360 --> 00:09:02.039
I don't believe you won't take action.

00:09:03.799 --> 00:09:05.120
Think about it carefully,

00:09:12.120 --> 00:09:12.759
Chengwen.

00:09:12.759 --> 00:09:13.559
Young Master.

00:09:14.639 --> 00:09:15.440
Brother Chengwen.

00:09:15.639 --> 00:09:16.720
Let's join forces.

00:09:16.759 --> 00:09:18.200
With the four major families of Haicheng together,

00:09:18.200 --> 00:09:19.559
I don't believe we can't deal with him.

00:09:19.799 --> 00:09:20.559
That's right.

00:09:20.559 --> 00:09:22.039
What's he so arrogant about?

00:09:23.320 --> 00:09:24.559
This is between him and me.

00:09:25.240 --> 00:09:26.360
It has nothing to do with you.

00:09:27.720 --> 00:09:28.519
You guys should leave.

00:09:29.200 --> 00:09:30.000
Zhao Gang,

00:09:30.559 --> 00:09:31.360
see them out.

00:09:32.320 --> 00:09:33.360
Let's go.

00:09:50.240 --> 00:09:51.039
Young Master.

00:09:52.960 --> 00:09:54.600
Has that thief been captured?

00:09:55.000 --> 00:09:55.799
Xuening.

00:09:56.639 --> 00:09:58.600
Do you know the joy of solving a puzzle?

00:10:00.000 --> 00:10:00.840
I think

00:10:01.840 --> 00:10:03.759
I'm getting close to the answer.

00:10:07.559 --> 00:10:08.240
That's right.

00:10:08.240 --> 00:10:09.600
I spent so much money,

00:10:09.840 --> 00:10:11.600
how could it proceed according to the original plan?

00:10:12.240 --> 00:10:13.039
President Zhao.

00:10:13.399 --> 00:10:14.200
Mr. Lu.

00:10:14.240 --> 00:10:15.279
This President Zhao

00:10:15.279 --> 00:10:17.039
suddenly calling us for an impromptu meeting,

00:10:17.320 --> 00:10:18.720
it must be

00:10:18.720 --> 00:10:20.440
because of the rumors spreading online that

00:10:20.440 --> 00:10:22.360
we're using the Chengnan project to scam money.

00:10:24.360 --> 00:10:25.960
Mr. Lu,

00:10:26.960 --> 00:10:28.039
what are you looking at?

00:10:30.240 --> 00:10:31.519
Looking at my past self.

00:10:37.600 --> 00:10:38.720
You corrupt bastards!

00:10:38.840 --> 00:10:39.639
Pay us back!

00:10:39.720 --> 00:10:40.519
Pay us back!

00:10:41.120 --> 00:10:41.919
Pay us back!

00:10:44.000 --> 00:10:44.759
Pay us back!

00:10:45.600 --> 00:10:46.399
Folks!

00:10:46.440 --> 00:10:47.399
The guy named Lu is here!

00:10:47.600 --> 00:10:48.120
He's here!

00:10:48.120 --> 00:10:48.919
The guy named Lu is here!

00:10:49.840 --> 00:10:50.360
Get down!

00:10:50.360 --> 00:10:50.759
Lu Chengwen!

00:10:50.759 --> 00:10:51.559
Get down here!

00:10:52.960 --> 00:10:53.720
What is the meaning of this?

00:10:53.720 --> 00:10:55.320
Give me back my hard-earned money!

00:10:55.440 --> 00:10:56.039
Pay us back!

00:10:56.039 --> 00:10:57.000
Get the hell out of Haicheng!

00:10:57.000 --> 00:10:57.519
Get out!

00:10:59.759 --> 00:11:00.399
Give me back my hard-earned money!

00:11:00.399 --> 00:11:01.200
Let go!

00:11:01.320 --> 00:11:02.120
You, surnamed Lu!

00:11:02.159 --> 00:11:03.120
Give us back our hard-earned money!

00:11:03.919 --> 00:11:04.720
Pay us back!

00:11:04.759 --> 00:11:05.200
Give me my money back!

00:11:05.200 --> 00:11:05.759
Hard-earned money!

00:11:05.759 --> 00:11:06.519
Give me back my hard-earned money!

00:11:06.720 --> 00:11:07.320
Hard-earned money!

00:11:07.320 --> 00:11:08.440
Give me back my hard-earned money!